  name: cdp-private-installer-docker-pull-secret
  namespace: nacho-cds    # <-- CHANGE THIS
Do the same for the ConfigMap YAML file.

üîπ Step 3: Apply to nacho-cds cluster
Now switch your oc CLI to the nacho-cds cluster:

bash
Copy
Edit
